      • setVouts

        public MoneroTxWallet setVouts(java.util.List<MoneroOutput> vouts)
        Set the tx's vouts (MoneroOutputWallet) which contain information relative to a wallet. Callers must cast to extended type (MoneroOutput) because Java paramaterized types do not recognize inheritance.
        Overrides:
        setVouts in class MoneroTx
        Parameters:
        vouts - are MoneroOutputWallets to set for the wallet tx
        Returns:
        MoneroTxWallet is a reference to this tx for chaining

      • merge

        public MoneroTxWallet merge(MoneroTxWallet tx)
        Updates this transaction by merging the latest information from the given transaction. Merging can modify or build references to the transaction given so it should not be re-used or it should be copied before calling this method.
        Parameters:
        tx - is the transaction to merge into this transaction
